&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/EUR-ROME-METAMORFOSI-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-7528&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/EUR-ROME-METAMORFOSI-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Loghi gruppo 3&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;86&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Located in the upscale residential neighborhood of Parioli, Metamorfosi has become a serious player on the international dining scene. Chef Roy &lt;span style=&quot;color: #262626;&quot;&gt;Caceres&lt;/span&gt;&nbsp;has earned a Michelin star for his menu that gradually changes with the season and according to the market. The contrast of concrete floors to floral banquettes give the dining room a soft, contemporary feel. Signature dishes such as the Carbonara Egg and Charcoal Grilled Glazed Eel are standouts. Flawless yet unpretentious service make guests feel welcome and cared for. Chic casual attire. &nbsp;(Photo Credit: Andrea Di Lorenzo)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Metamorfosi by phone at +39-06-807-6839 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:reservation@metamorfosiroma.it&quot;&gt;reservation@metamorfosiroma.it&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

